Class InstancesDao

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.odk.collect.android.dao.InstancesDao

  • public class InstancesDao
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to encapsulate all access to the org.odk.collect.android.provider.InstanceProvider#DATABASE_NAME For more information about this pattern go to https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Data_access_object
